{"id":150810,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/伊拉克一所监狱发生骚乱事件/","date":"2011-05-08T16:00:16Z","modified":"2011-05-08T16:00:16Z","title":"伊拉克一所监狱发生骚乱事件","content":"<div>\n<p><span><br /></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">巴格达</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周日（</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>8</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）在伊拉克首都巴格达一所监狱发生的骚乱事件中有至少</span><span>18</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人丧生，其中</span><span>11</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">名狱犯、</span><span>7</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">名监管人员。巴格达市安全当局一名发言人称，死者中包括被称为“巴格达埃米尔”的基地组织头目之一的巴塔维（</span><span>Huthaifa al-Batawi</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）。巴塔维受到指控，策划了</span><span>2010</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年</span><span>10</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月导致</span><span>50</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多人丧生的对一座基督教堂的袭击。自基地组织第一号头目本拉登本周一凌晨在巴基斯坦被美军击毙以来，因担心发生报复行动，伊拉克安全力量在全国进入了戒备状态。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15059511%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%89%80%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E9%AA%9A%E4%B9%B1%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name